@startuml
title 3.2 Technischer Kontext - Data Processing

top to bottom direction

package "PC / Laptop" {
    component "GUI (PyQt6)" as UI
    component "Logic (Python)" as Logic
    component "Vision (OpenCV)" as CV

    UI <--> Logic : Status & Bilder
    Logic <--> CV : Bilddaten (Arrays)
}

database "Dateisystem" as HDD

Logic <-- HDD : **T1**: Lese Bild
Logic --> HDD : **T2**: Schreibe Log

note right of Logic
  Core Intelligence:
  - Analyzer
  - Edge Solver
  - Assembler
end note

@enduml